得多么乐，多么欢；</p><p>  \t我们的教员是英雄，</p><p>  \t曾毕业在草地雪山。</p><p>  \t我们也学种菜，学背柴，</p><p>  \t还到乡村里宣传；</p><p>  \t多流一滴汗，</p><p>  \t多学得一点马列，</p><p>  \t多到群众里工作，</p><p>  \t多学得一些群众观点。</p><p>  \t深更半夜，工作归来，</p><p>  \t头顶明月，脚踩沙滩，</p><p>  \t哼着歌子，绕过延水边&mdash;&mdash;</p><p>  \t呵！唱不尽的是革命，</p><p>  \t看不厌的是明月，</p><p>  \t我们年青人的热情，</p><p>  \t好比流不尽的水，</p><p>  \t留连，留连，</p><p>  \t夜深了，还在延水边留连。</p><p>  \t忽见中央机关那一面，</p><p>  \t还有星星大的灯光三五点，</p><p>  \t那分明是老干部还在窑洞里埋头苦干，</p><p>  \t又才警觉到战斗的明天。</p><p>  \t明天，明天同样是战斗的学习，战斗的工作，战斗的生产；</p><p>  \t战斗的青年。</p><p>  \t要带着毛主席给的战斗法宝，</p><p>  \t到前线，</p><p>  \t到广大的民间。</p><p></p><p>  \t啊！青年！青年！</p><p>  \t勇敢的中国青年！</p><p>  \t多情的中国青年！</p><p>  \t你穿破了延安的草鞋，</p><p>  \t你取得了一些活生生的革命经典，</p><p>  \t你吃饱了延安的小米饭，</p><p>  \t你有了一个能思想的脑袋。</p><p>  \t你呀你，你前进！</p><p>  \t你将开花在华北华南，</p><p>  \t结实在鸭绿江边，</p><p>  \t青年！你可爱的中国青年！</p><p>1939年秋在延安</p>","createBy":"35988","createName":null,"createTime":"2022-10-21T10:00:32","decipherment":null,"deleted":false,"difficultyId":null,"difficultyName":null,"gradeId":null,"id":"790035880529105109","isCharged":false,"isGroupQuestion":true,"isSubjective":false,"lineNumber":1,"oldId":null,"optionA":null,"optionB":null,"optionC":null,"optionD":null,"optionE":null,"optionF":null,"optionG":null,"options":[],"origin":1,"paperTypeId":null,"parentId":"0","pickCount":0,"provinceId":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionSerialNo":3058310,"questionVideo":null,"relateKnowledge":null,"scoreBasis":null,"source":null,"title":null,"typeDetailId":"6","typeDetailName":"简答题","typeId":"12","typeName":"现当代诗歌阅读","updateBy":"35988","updateName":null,"updateTime":"2022-10-21T10:00:32","uploadBatch":"1666317632016","yearId":null},"questionId":null,"questionNumber":null},{"answer":null,"answerStatus":null,"childQuestionList":[{"answer":null,"answerStatus":6,"childQuestionList":null,"chooseGroup":null,"chooseGroupQuestionList":null,"isAnswer":false,"isChooseGroup":null,"isGroupQuestion":null,"isMistake":null,"ordered":14,"question":{"answer":"A","answerExplanation":"","cityId":null,"content